Description:
Park Front in BERWICK WATERS!
Located in popular Berwick Waters Estate, this proudly presented family home offers a blend of space & charm all in one stunning package that your family will enjoy for many years to come.
If quality living and entertaining is high on your priority list then this immaculate property is certainly worthy of inspection.
Located within walking distance to Tulliallan Primary school, St Catherines Catholic Primary School, St Francis Xavier College, bus stops, shopping centre, parks and waterfronts at your doorstep, this perfectly positioned delight is ideal for the growing family. With quality fitting and fixtures throughout, the house's interior comprises a master bedroom to the front of the house with walk in robe and ensuite, two more bedrooms with built in robes and a main bathroom to keep rest of the family satisfied. Rich floating boards flow from the front entrance hall into the heart of the home, to the huge open plan living/dining/ kitchen. You'll enjoy every minute in this centrally located chefs' kitchen showcasing stylish cabinets,walk-in pantry, 900mm stainless steel 5 burner cooktop & oven, dishwasher and expansive Caesarstone benchtop with breakfast bar overlooking the dining and living areas ideal for keeping an eye on the kids. Enjoy fabulous family quality time in separate living/ lounge area. Journey outside to find a sensational covered alfresco providing the ultimate lifestyle to entertain family and friends, whilst surrounded by a manicured landscaped garden with grassed area.
Your new home in Berwick Waters comes with
- Two separate living zones
- LED Downlights to Hallway, kitchen, livings and dining areas
- Elegant floating boards to Hallway & open plan living,dining and kitchen
- Quality carpets to bedrooms and lounge/ theatre room
- Double lockup garage with internal access to house.
- 900mm Five burner cooktop and oven
- Window & Glass splash back
- Walkin pantry to kitchen
- Ducted Heating
- Evaporate Cooling
- Stone benchtop with breakfast bar to Kitchen
- Stone benchtops to ensuite and Bathroom
- Designer front and back landscaping
This house is in walking distance to
- Tulliallan Primary school
- St Francis Xavier College, Berwick Campus
- Berwick Chase Primary School
- St Catherines Catholic Primary School
- Water front
- Multiple parks
- Grices Road Recreation Reserve
- Waterside shopping Centre
- Bus stop (route 899)
And in short drive to
- Hillcrest and Rivercrest Christian College
- Eden Rise Village
- Bunnings Clyde North
- Berwick train station
- Berwick town centre
- Access to Monash freeway
Call Dilshan 0402 696 602 or Ravi on 0444 522 762 to schedule a private inspection for you to flow through the house at your own phase with no distractions and feel all this home has to offer.

Description:
Berwick Waters Delight
Contact agent for private inspection.
Immaculately presented and positioned this home is perfect. Whether you're a first home buyer or looking for that ideal investment, or after a downsize this one will tick all your boxes.
Comprising of three bedrooms with master including walk in robe and ensuite while the remaining two bedrooms provide ample floor space and one provides a walk in robe and the other boasts sizeable built in robe. Both are well positioned near the main bathroom and toilet. Downstairs is so light and airy with larger windows accompanying the living, meals, kitchen area and powder room. The kitchen itself is well appointed and is sure to impress the chef, with stainless steel appliances, 900mm oven and stove, dishwasher and walk in pantry. Ceaser Stone benchtops and an abundance of storage to finish of the kitchen.
Outside you are welcomed with a corner block, low maintenance gardens and a double remote access garage with internal access. Newly finished fencing all round just makes you realise how young this home is.
Creature comforts also include ducted heating, two split air cons, ducted vacuum, high ceilings to lower level, sprinkler system to front and rear, gas solar panels and roller shutters to lower level and master bedrooms.
Located in the Berwick Waters estate you are closely located to Primary and Secondary Schools, Eden Rise Shopping Village, public transport, parks and hospital and medical centers. What more could you be looking for in a home.
Contact agent for private inspection.

Description:
TITLED LAND POSITIONED FOR GROWTH IN ST.GERMAIN ESTATE
30 RANGER STREET, CLYDE NORTH
Titled land 448sqm, start building your HOME instantly
14m frontage X 32m depth
VILLAGE LIFE, URBAN STYLE, MODERN CONVENIENCE
A beautiful place to live, a community that has something to offer everyone. St Germain is located on Thompsons Road, just 10 minutes from the Princes Freeway (M1) and Berwick. Part of the booming South-eastern corridor, it is only 45 minutes from Melbourne's CBD and 30 minutes from the beautiful coastal towns of the Mornington Peninsula.
Master-planned with ready infrastructure, everything you could ever need is just minutes away. Shopping, recreation and quality education are close by, not to mention easy access to public transport and other facilities i.e. Hillcrest Christian College, Rivercrest College, Eden Rise Shopping Centre, Old Berwick Post Office, Monash University, Cranbourne Golf Course, Berwick Railway Station.
Infrastructure at St Germain already in place and unlike most new development projects, construction of the Town Centre will begin concurrently. Inspired by a contemporary European village lifestyle, St Germain is all about living, working, shopping, and socialising, all in one place. St Germain will offer a vibrant retail strip, modern offices, as well as plans for a retirement village, and regional medical centre with job opportunities expected to emerge in the near future.
A WELL-CONNECTED LIFESTYLE
Proposed Town Centre with major supermarket and 12 retail shops, alongside restaurants,
cafes, childcare facilities, a gym, and office space. Lifestyle Village and Clubhouse will offer independent living options with over 250 dwellings. A central clubhouse will provide recreational facilities such as tennis courts and lawn bowling, offering a premium living experience.
You don't want to miss this beautiful opportunity so please call Vinny on 0449 058 007 to book an appointment.
Photo ID is a must.

Description:
SOLD BY TEAM ANDREW 0411 735 776
Looking for a home with absolutely everything? You are in luck because 110 Moxham Drive with 5 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms and the large backyard, this home is everything you've have wished for.
At the heart of this home is a delightful chef's kitchen which is fitted out with quality stainless steel appliances, ample storage space, stone benchtops and not one but two walk in pantries. This kitchen overlooks the family/living area, separate dining and outdoor entertaining area.
Downstairs accomodation also includes a master suite with ensuite and WIR.
Upstairs, there's plenty of space for the entire family. It includes two master suites, two additional bedrooms and a guest bathroom. These rooms all circle a large family retreat. The main master bedroom includes a his and hers wardrobe, double vanity ensuite and an oversized shower.
The home also includes ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ducted vacuum, CCTV with mobile connectivity, a Ring doorbell and double lock up garage.
This is literally a home you can move in and jump straight into bed. This property is close to major schools including Wilandra Rise Primary School and Casey Grammar School. It is only a moments drive to Shopping on Clyde and major arterials including the Monash and Princes Freeway.
Book an inspection today with Team Andrew on 0411 735 776.

Description:
Elegant Fairhaven Ex-Display Home
Situated in the highly popular Berwick Waters Estate is this exceptional abode, located in a street of high end display homes, you are surrounded by the best! Family friendly, with display quality clearly on show, this ex-display Fairhaven Clovelly 276 home is perfect for that buyer wanting a touch of class.
On offer are 4 generous size bedrooms including master with a sophisticated en-suite and a WIR. The remaining three bedrooms are serviced by BIR and a modern family bathroom.
The open plan living is the heart of the home, the kitchen with stainless steel appliances and dishwasher, stone bench tops as well as ample bench and cupboard space with a walk-in pantry, with the family meals area adjacent.
Other features of the property include refrigerated cooling and ducted heating, remote to DLUG and an outstanding outdoor area, decked and impeccably landscaped.
Enjoy the best of what Clyde North & Berwick has to offer with close proximity to prestigious schools, Casey Central & Eden Rise shopping centre, public transport and medical and sport facilities.

Description:
PREMIUM FEATURES IN PRIME LOCATION
INSPECTION THIS SATURDAY 13th 12:30pm-1:00pm
This stylish and immaculately presented home exudes quality and is perfect for the young family or downsizer. Located in the prized Cascades on Clyde Estate, this 6-year-old, architecturally influenced Arden built home boasts many premium upgrades. It features open plan living areas with elevated ceilings and doors, an oversized master bed bedroom with stunning walk in robe and double basin vanity en-suite, home theatre room, additional workshop, outdoor alfresco, Smeg appliances, solar panels, security system and dual driveways with ample side access to park your boat or caravan. Its premium living at its finest.
Undoubtedly the heart of the home is centred around its open plan living that creates the perfect space for entertaining. Overseeing the lounge and dining areas is the extremely well-appointed kitchen that boasts luxury branded Smeg appliances, an oversized island stone benchtop and breakfast bar, custom tiled splashback, premium lighting, a generous walk in pantry and 900mm stainless steel oven with range hood.
Also presenting with stunning appeal is the front master bed-suite. Sitting to the front of the house, its set apart with its generous proportions and is an idyllic parents retreat. Featuring an oversized walk in robe, large en-suite with double basin vanity, spacious 1800mm custom tiled shower and separate toilet. Its unparalleled at this price point.
Entertaining is also breeze as the rear living space encompasses a second living area that was designed as dedicated home theatre room. (currently being used as a home office). This area is surrounded by the remaining 2 bedrooms that are serviced by the large main bathroom, creating the perfect kids entertaining zone.
Lastly, the outdoor space continues to impress, with a large under the roof line alfresco that extends the indoor to the out effortlessly. Presenting with low maintenance gardens and dedicated bbq area you can switch off and simply enjoy entertaining with your family and friends.
This property is simply not to be missed.
Other features include:
- Ducted Heating
- Evaporative cooling
- 8kw Split System Air conditioning
- 5.1kw/10 Panel Solar Power (New)
- LED Downlights
- Security System/Alarm
- TV points all main rooms
- Double Car Lock up Garage
- Workshop
- Floating floors
Located close to all amenities including schools, shops, transport and parks this property has it all! With exacting quality, sophisticated styling and a prized location an inspection is a must.
BOOK YOUR INSPECTION TODAY

Description:
Modern, Spacious, Quality Build.
Located in the small, elevated Circa estate adjacent to Berwick Waters, a meticulously presented, quality build with numerous upgrades. Welcomed by an attractive modern faÃ§ade and flourishing landscape this property is perfect for the buyer searching for a home that is ready to move in and to be enjoyed. Downstairs boasts, study/sitting room, open plan living with atmospheric living flame remote controlled gas log fire and dining room, modern hostess kitchen detailed with stone benchtops, quality stainless steel appliances, boiling water tap, feature sliding barn door for pantry and an abundance of cupboard space. Additionally, a revamped laundry used for additional pantry space with all the upgrades including stone benchtop. Upstairs discover sleeping accommodation which consists of grand master suite with walk in robe and ensuite with double vanities, the perfect parents' retreat. Remaining two bedrooms generous in size offer built in robes and are serviced by stylish main bathroom.
Access through double sliding doors to a fabulous decked alfresco and covered pergola, surrounded by decorative woodwork, metal shutters to side of alfresco, sensational landscaping, hidden garden lighting and water feature, creating a private and tranquil zone.
Creature comforts include; remote controlled ceiling fans, ducted heating, air conditioning to family room/kitchen, plantation shutters to front and side plus venetians to remaining windows, aggregate to front and sides of the abode, higher spec insulation and additional ducted heating vents to both bathrooms.
Enjoy an award winning park and other amenities within proximity to Circa Estate, including prestigious schools, Eden Rise shopping centre, medical facilities, and so much more.
This much loved, well cared for opulent built home is ready for your inspection, enquire today and make it yours tomorrow!
Photo I.D required at all inspections.
